n--plain">2,699 人<!-- -->赞同了该回答</button></span></div></div><meta itemProp="image" content=""/><meta itemProp="upvoteCount" content="2699"/><meta itemProp="url" content="https://www.zhihu.com/question/265479096/answer/296303267"/><meta itemProp="dateCreated" content="2018-01-15T09:32:09.000Z"/><meta itemProp="dateModified" content="2018-01-15T09:32:09.000Z"/><meta itemProp="commentCount" content="169"/><div class="RichContent is-collapsed"><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">任何一个组织，不给下面通过奋斗而上升的渠道，这个组织必然丧失活力，乃至生命力。 但《水浒传》中的梁山，显然是没有这样渠道的，当了喽啰就是喽啰，大哥就是大哥，没有一个当了喽啰还能成为大哥的。这也太固化了吧。为啥会这样呢?我曾经百撕不得骑姐，还一度认为是施耐庵缺少见识。后来才知道，缺少见识的是我。 其实，这个答案，晁盖已经给出了。在安排劫生辰纲的人手之前吴用说 〖只是一件，人多做不得，人少又做不得。宅上…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->2.7K</button><button aria-label="反对" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--down"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleDown" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" w